local Ladder = require "object/Ladder" return function(self, player) Ladder.notColliding(self, player)
for _, layer in pairs(self.scene.map.layers) do if layer.name == "tempoverlay1" then layer.opacity = 0.0 end end end

local Ladder = require "object/Ladder" return function(self, player) Ladder.whileColliding(self, player)
for _, layer in pairs(self.scene.map.layers) do if layer.name == "tempoverlay1" then layer.opacity = 1.0 end end end
